+// These are the canonical IDs for the two-level beads architecture:
+// - Town-level agents (Mayor, Deacon, Dogs) → ~/gt/.beads/ with hq- prefix
+// - Rig-level agents (Witness, Refinery, Polecats) → <rig>/.beads/ with rig prefix
